{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b6977-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8621"},"text":"§ 8621.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Home energy grants","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b6978-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary is authorized to make grants, in accordance with the provisions of this subchapter, to States to assist low-income households, particularly those with the lowest incomes, that pay a high proportion of household income for home energy, primarily in meeting their immediate home energy needs.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b6979-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out the provisions of this subchapter (other than ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":"), $2,000,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1995 through 1999, such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2000 and 2001, and $5,100,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2005 through 2007. The authorizations of appropriations contained in this subsection are subject to the program year provisions of subsection (c)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Availability of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amounts appropriated under this section for any fiscal year for programs and activities under this subchapter shall be made available for obligation in the succeeding fiscal year.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations for leveraged resources","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":", $30,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1999 through 2004, except as provided in paragraph (2)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For any of fiscal years 1999 through 2004 for which the amount appropriated under subsection (b) is not less than $1,400,000,000, there is authorized to be appropriated $50,000,000 to carry out ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s8621/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Emergency funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There is authorized to be appropriated in each fiscal year for payments under this subchapter, in addition to amounts appropriated for distribution to all the States in accordance with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8623"},"text":"section 8623 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (other than subsection (e) of such section), $600,000,000 to meet the additional home energy assistance needs of one or more States arising from a natural disaster or other emergency. Funds appropriated pursuant to this subsection are hereby designated to be emergency requirements pursuant to section 251(b)(2)(D) of the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s901/b/2/D"},"text":"2 U.S.C. 901(b)(2)(D)","children":[],"tail":"], except that such funds shall be made available only after the submission to Congress of a formal budget request by the President (for all or a part of the appropriation pursuant to this subsection) that includes a designation of the amount requested as an emergency requirement as defined in such Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s900"},"text":"2 U.S.C. 900","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbe9b697f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tXXVI/s2602"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title XXVI, § 2602","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/893"},"text":"95 Stat. 893","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/558/tVI/s601"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–558, title VI, § 601","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-30"},"text":"Oct. 30, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/2889"},"text":"98 Stat. 2889","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/425/tV/s501"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–425, title V, § 501","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/973"},"text":"100 Stat. 973","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/tVII"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, title VII","children":[],"tail":", §§ 701, 702, 707(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-03"},"text":"Nov. 3, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/1258"},"text":"104 Stat. 1258","children":[],"tail":", 1261; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/43/tXX/s2011"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–43, title XX, § 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-06-10"},"text":"June 10, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/214"},"text":"107 Stat. 214","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/tIII"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, title III","children":[],"tail":", §§ 302–304(a), 311(c)(1), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-05-18"},"text":"May 18, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/657"},"text":"108 Stat. 657","children":[],"tail":", 658, 661; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/285/tIII/s302"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–285, title III, § 302","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-27"},"text":"Oct. 27, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2756"},"text":"112 Stat. 2756","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/58/tI/s121/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–58, title I, § 121(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2005-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 2005","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/119/616"},"text":"119 Stat. 616","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbe9b6980-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbe9b6981-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbe9b6982-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 251 of the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985, referred to in subsec. (e), is classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s901"},"text":"section 901 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":", The Congress. Section 251 was amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/33/tX/s10203/a/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–33, title X, § 10203(a)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/699"},"text":"111 Stat. 699","children":[],"tail":", and by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/25/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–25, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-08-02"},"text":"Aug. 2, 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/125/241"},"text":"125 Stat. 241","children":[],"tail":". As so amended, section 251(b)(2)(D) no longer refers to “emergency requirements”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985, referred to in subsec. (e), is title II of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/177"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–177","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-12"},"text":"Dec. 12, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/1038"},"text":"99 Stat. 1038","children":[],"tail":", which enacted chapter 20 (§ 900 et seq.) and sections 654 to 656 of Title 2, The Congress, amended sections 602, 622, 631 to 642, and 651 to 653 of Title 2, sections 1104 to 1106, and 1109 of Title 31, Money and Finance, and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s911"},"text":"section 911 of this title","children":[],"tail":", repealed "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s661"},"text":"section 661 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":", enacted provisions set out as notes under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s900"},"text":"section 900 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s911"},"text":"section 911 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and amended provisions set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s621"},"text":"section 621 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s900"},"text":"section 900 of Title 2","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbe9b6983-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2005—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/58"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–58","children":[],"tail":" substituted “and $5,100,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2005 through 2007” for “and $2,000,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2002 through 2004”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/285/s302/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–285, § 302(a)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “, such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2000 and 2001, and $2,000,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2002 through 2004” after “1995 through 1999”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/285/s302/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–285, § 302(b)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (c) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (c) read as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(c)(1) In fiscal year 1993 and each fiscal year thereafter, amounts appropriated under this section for any fiscal year for programs and activities under this subchapter shall be made available for obligation only on the basis of a program year. The program year shall begin on October 1 of the fiscal year following the year in which the appropriation is made.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) Amounts appropriated for fiscal year 1993 shall be available both to fund activities for the period between ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1992","children":[],"tail":", and "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1993","children":[],"tail":", and for the program year beginning "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1993","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) There are authorized to be appropriated such additional sums as may be necessary for the transition to carry out this subsection.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/285/s302/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–285, § 302(c)","children":[],"tail":", designated existing provisions as par. (1), substituted “There is authorized” for “There are authorized” and “$30,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1999 through 2004, except as provided in paragraph (2)” for “$50,000,000 for each of the fiscal years 1996 and 1997, and such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1998 and 1999”, and added par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/285/s302/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–285, § 302(d)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “There is authorized” for “There are authorized” and “(other than subsection (e) of such section)” for “(other than subsection (g))”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/s302"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, § 302","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (a) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (a) read as follows: “The Secretary of Health and Human Services is authorized to make grants, in accordance with the provisions of this subchapter, to States to assist eligible households to meet the costs of home energy.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252","children":[],"tail":", §§ 303(a)(1), 311(c)(1)(A), substituted “this subchapter (other than "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":"), $2,000,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1995 through 1999” for “this subchapter (other than "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":") $2,307,000,000 for fiscal year 1990, $2,150,000,000 for fiscal year 1991, $2,230,000,000 for fiscal year 1992, and such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1993, 1994, and 1995” and struck out second period at end."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/s311/c/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, § 311(c)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", made technical amendment to reference to this subchapter to correct reference to corresponding provision of original act."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/s303/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, § 303(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", which directed the substitution of “October 1” for “July 1” and “following the year in which” for “for which” in last sentence of subsec. (c), was executed by making the substitutions in last sentence of subsec. (c)(1) to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/s303/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, § 303(b)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (d) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (d) read as follows: “There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":", $25,000,000 in fiscal year 1992, and $50,000,000 for each of the fiscal years 1993, 1994, and 1995.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/s304/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, § 304(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1993—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/43/s2011/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–43, § 2011(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “1993, 1994, and 1995” for “1993 and 1994”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/43/s2011/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–43, § 2011(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “for each of the fiscal years 1993, 1994, and 1995” for “in each of the fiscal years 1993 and 1994”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/s707/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, § 707(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", which directed the amendment of this section by inserting “(other than "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s8626a"},"text":"section 8626a of this title","children":[],"tail":")” after “subchapter”, was executed to subsec. (b) to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/s702"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, § 702","children":[],"tail":", struck out “$2,050,000,000 for fiscal year 1987, $2,132,000,000 for fiscal year 1988, $2,218,000,000 for fiscal year 1989, and” before “$2,307,000,000” and inserted “, $2,150,000,000 for fiscal year 1991, $2,230,000,000 for fiscal year 1992, and such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1993 and 1994. The authorizations of appropriations contained in this subsection are subject to the program year provisions of subsection (c).” after “1990”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/s701"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, § 701","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/s707/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, § 707(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/425"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–425","children":[],"tail":" amended subsec. (b) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (b) read as follows: “There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out the provisions of this subchapter $2,140,000,000 for the fiscal year 1985, and $2,275,000,000 for the fiscal year 1986.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1984—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/558"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–558","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$2,140,000,000 for fiscal year 1985, and $2,275,000,000 for fiscal year 1986” for “$1,875,000,000 for each of fiscal years 1982, 1983, and 1984”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idbe9b6984-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idbe9b6985-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1994 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/252/tIII/s314"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–252, title III, § 314","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-05-18"},"text":"May 18, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/666"},"text":"108 Stat. 666","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/103/252/tIII/s314"},"text":"“The amendments and repeals made by this title [see Short Title of 1994 Amendment note below] shall become effective on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1994","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idbe9b6986-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1990 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/501/tX/s1001"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–501, title X, § 1001","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-03"},"text":"Nov. 3, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/1283"},"text":"104 Stat. 1283","children":[],"tail":", provided that:"},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/101/501/tX/s1001"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"“(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"General Effective Date","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in subsection (b), this Act and the amendments made by this Act [see Tables for classification] shall take effect on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1990","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"“(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Special Effective Dates","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The amendment made by section 207(b) [repealing a provision set out as a note preceding ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s9861"},"text":"section 9861 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] shall take effect immediately before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1990","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"ta